entries.journal_entry_description: I'm actually working for Captain Dustrunner. He thinks I'm his long lost undercover agent. I'll have to do whatever I can to keep him happy until I get Borvo's information settled.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: I have to go see Maerzen, who supposedly has evidence that will convict Borvo and his men. I need to make sure that evidence never gets to CorSec.
entries.task01_message_box_text: This is the drop point where Maerzen is supposed to deliver the evidence. Look around and see if you can find him.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: I have to make sure Maerzen doesn't let that evidence fall into CorSec's hands.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to tell Captain Dustrunner something that explains how I ended up with the evidence, and Maerzen's not with me. I'll think of something on my way back.
